#define R(p,a,t) mix(a*dot(p,a),p,cos(t))+sin(t)*cross(p,a)
#define H(h) (cos((h)*6.3+vec3(0,23,21))*.5+.5)

void mainImage(out vec4 O, in vec2 C)
{
    O=vec4(0);
	vec3 p,r=iResolution,
    d=normalize(vec3((C-.5*r.xy)/r.y,1));
    float i=0.,g=0.,e,s,t=iTime;
	for(;i++<90.;){
        p=d*g;
        p.z-=1.8;
        p=R(p,normalize(H(t*.05)+sin(t*30.)*2e-3),t*.2);
        e=s=2.;
        for(int i=0;i++<7;)
            p=.1-abs(abs(p)-.3),
            p=p.x<p.y?p.zxy:p.zyx,
            e=min(e,(length(vec2(length(p.xy)-1.,p.z)))/s+5e-4),
            s*=2.,
            p*=2.,
            p-=vec3(-.8,.2,.5*sin(t*.3));
        g+=e;
        O.rgb+=mix(vec3(1),H(p.z*.4+sin(t*.5+sin(t*20.))),.5)*.13/exp(i*i*e);
    }
    O*=O*O;    
}
